I was sitting around watching videos, and the idea of, "hey, what if I had a large magnetic ring( my heads thinking Captain America shield size, or something a little more reasonable), and attempted to create plasma? Would it fill in the rings open space with plasma, creating a sort of wall? If so, how strong would it be? Would it light things on fire if it touched them? These are the questions I think of at 1:30 am watching plasma molding demonstration videos.
